: : Rodimus Prime / Kup : :

Rodimus recieved a comm message. When he activated it a holographic image of Galvatron appeared. It was perjected by the comm system in his wrist. After it ended Rodimus looked inraged.

Rodimus Prime: Ahhhhhhhh! I&#39;ll get youuuuuuuuuuuu!

Rodimus slams his fist intoa large boulder near by. The boulder crumbles around the Autobot&#39;s fist.

Rodimus Prime: He thinks this is fun, Kup. When it comes down to just him and I, I&#39;ll take him down for good. I didn&#39;t get it done before, but I&#39;ll make sure of it now...

Kup: Calm down, lad. I know how you feel. i&#39;ve been with you a long time Rody, I&#39;ve seen all the crap he&#39;s done. You&#39;ll get him, and I&#39;ll be the first to congradulate you.

Rodimus Prime: Thanks old friend.
