  From: aerosmith60@... 
  To: nbwrpg@yahoogroups.com 
  Sent: Tuesday, August 13, 2002 7:40 PM
  Subject: Rodimus, Quilldart, Galvatron


  Galvatron saw  Quilldart jet towards the base. &quot;Good no doubt the other two are not far behind.&quot; He sent a comm to Rodimus. A holographic image of himself would display. &quot;I am so glad Rodimus we could come to terms. As for our one on one battle. Dont you worry. That will happen in due time. Until then best of luck my old friend. I havent had this much fun since our little unicron adventure...wouldnt you agree?&quot; He ended the comm and turned back to the map. He had his three blips on the screen. 
